WEBVTT 

00:00:00.640 --> 00:00:03.240
When children went to school,

00:00:03.320 --> 00:00:07.440
they called their parents
and said they were feeling ill.

00:00:07.520 --> 00:00:09.160
Parents messaged each other

00:00:09.240 --> 00:00:12.560
that their children had a poisoning
and they were fainting.

00:00:13.200 --> 00:00:15.360
By 11 o'clock, there were 68 children

00:00:15.440 --> 00:00:20.240
in central hospitals in the area.

